planet1

public double planet1(double x,
                      double y,
                      double z)
Top level of planetary terrain generation. This carries out the first level of subdivision and returns the height of a point

Parameters:
x - The x coordinate of the point to get altitude for
y - The y coordinate of the point to get altitude for
z - The z coordinate of the point to get altitude for
Returns:
The altiude of the planet at this point (0 = sea level)
